---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Navbar from "../components/Navbar.jsx";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Services"
  page="services"
  description="IT services for small and medium businesses—strategy, security, and cloud—with a free initial consultation."
>
  <Navbar client:load />

  <main class="page-main">
    <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 md:py-20">
      <div class="glass rounded-3xl glow p-8 md:p-10">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-white">Services</h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg md:text-xl" style="color: var(--muted);">
          Choose a single engagement or combine services into a tailored plan. Every engagement includes clear scope and measurable outcomes.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a href="/contact"
             class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 rounded-xl font-extrabold transition hover:brightness-110"
             style="background: var(--color-accent-green); color: #08110c; box-shadow: 0 0 22px rgba(57,255,122,0.22);">
            Book a free consult
          </a>
          <a href="/case-studies"
             class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 rounded-xl font-bold border border-white/15 bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/15 transition text-white">
            View case studies
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 pb-24">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="glass rounded-2xl glow p-6 md:col-span-3">
          <div class="text-sm font-bold" style="color: var(--color-accent-purple);">Prime strategic service</div>
          <h2 class="text-white font-extrabold text-2xl mt-2">IT Strategy &amp; Roadmap Planning</h2>
          <p class="mt-3" style="color: var(--muted);">
            Structured 1–5 year technology planning across architecture, network, platforms/SaaS and cybersecurity—vendor-neutral and outcome-focused.
          </p>
          <a href="/it-strategy-roadmap"
             class="mt-5 inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 rounded-xl font-extrabold transition hover:brightness-110"
             style="background: var(--color-accent-green); color: #08110c; box-shadow: 0 0 22px rgba(57,255,122,0.22);">
            View IT Roadmap Service
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="glass rounded-2xl glow p-6">
          <div class="text-sm font-bold" style="color: var(--color-accent-purple);">Fractional leadership</div>
          <h2 class="text-white font-extrabold text-xl mt-2">Virtual CTO (Fractional)</h2>
          <p class="mt-3" style="color: var(--muted);">
            Senior tech leadership without a full-time hire—prioritisation, governance, vendors, and delivery confidence.
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-4 list-disc pl-5 space-y-2" style="color: var(--muted);">
            <li>Strategy and roadmap</li>
            <li>Vendor evaluation and management</li>
            <li>Delivery oversight and reporting</li>
            <li>Budgeting and prioritisation</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="glass rounded-2xl glow p-6">
          <div class="text-sm font-bold" style="color: var(--color-accent-purple);">Architecture & cloud</div>
          <h2 class="text-white font-extrabold text-xl mt-2">Cloud & Systems Architecture</h2>
          <p class="mt-3" style="color: var(--muted);">
            Secure, scalable foundations that reduce cost and support growth—without unnecessary complexity.
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-4 list-disc pl-5 space-y-2" style="color: var(--muted);">
            <li>Target architecture & migration plans</li>
            <li>Reliability, backups, and DR readiness</li>
            <li>Cloud cost control (FinOps basics)</li>
            <li>Integrations and modern patterns</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="glass rounded-2xl glow p-6">
          <div class="text-sm font-bold" style="color: var(--color-accent-purple);">Risk & resilience</div>
          <h2 class="text-white font-extrabold text-xl mt-2">Cyber Risk Reduction</h2>
          <p class="mt-3" style="color: var(--muted);">
            Practical uplift focused on the controls that reduce risk fastest—aligned to your business priorities.
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-4 list-disc pl-5 space-y-2" style="color: var(--muted);">
            <li>MFA, access control, least privilege</li>
            <li>Logging, monitoring, alerting</li>
            <li>Backup verification and recovery drills</li>
            <li>Policies and incident readiness</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="glass rounded-2xl glow p-6">
          <div class="text-sm font-bold" style="color: var(--color-accent-purple);">Delivery confidence</div>
          <h2 class="text-white font-extrabold text-xl mt-2">Project & Program Oversight</h2>
          <p class="mt-3" style="color: var(--muted);">
            Keep initiatives on track with clear milestones, accountability, and quality checks—especially with vendors.
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-4 list-disc pl-5 space-y-2" style="color: var(--muted);">
            <li>Project setup and success metrics</li>
            <li>Cadence, reporting, escalation</li>
            <li>Risk/issue management</li>
            <li>Go-live readiness</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="glass rounded-2xl glow p-6">
          <div class="text-sm font-bold" style="color: var(--color-accent-purple);">AI enablement</div>
          <h2 class="text-white font-extrabold text-xl mt-2">AI & Automation</h2>
          <p class="mt-3" style="color: var(--muted);">
            Safe, sensible AI adoption—reduce admin load, improve support, and accelerate workflows with governance.
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-4 list-disc pl-5 space-y-2" style="color: var(--muted);">
            <li>Use-case discovery and ROI sizing</li>
            <li>Tool selection and rollout plan</li>
            <li>Workflow automation & integration</li>
            <li>Governance and staff enablement</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="glass rounded-2xl glow p-6">
          <div class="text-sm font-bold" style="color: var(--color-accent-purple);">Clarity fast</div>
          <h2 class="text-white font-extrabold text-xl mt-2">Technology Health Check</h2>
          <p class="mt-3" style="color: var(--muted);">
            A short engagement to identify quick wins, risks, and priorities—perfect before committing to a big project.
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-4 list-disc pl-5 space-y-2" style="color: var(--muted);">
            <li>Current-state review</li>
            <li>Risk and cost hotspots</li>
            <li>90-day action plan</li>
            <li>Roadmap recommendations</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>


      <section class="mt-10 glass rounded-3xl glow p-8 md:p-10">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white">How Aurora ICT works</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg" style="color: var(--muted);">
          Aurora ICT works as a practical, modular advisory journey. Start with the support you need, continue only where it adds value, and stop at any stage once your business has the clarity, structure, and confidence to move forward.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-8 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-6">
            <h3 class="text-white font-extrabold text-xl">1. Assess</h3>
            <p class="mt-3" style="color: var(--muted);">
              Understand costs, risks, systems, vendors, and immediate priorities.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-6">
            <h3 class="text-white font-extrabold text-xl">2. Prioritise</h3>
            <p class="mt-3" style="color: var(--muted);">
              Turn findings into practical actions, quick wins, and a realistic plan.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-6">
            <h3 class="text-white font-extrabold text-xl">3. Support</h3>
            <p class="mt-3" style="color: var(--muted);">
              Provide targeted advisory help where it adds value across projects, vendors, security, and delivery.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-6">
            <h3 class="text-white font-extrabold text-xl">4. Simplify</h3>
            <p class="mt-3" style="color: var(--muted);">
              Leave the business with clearer ownership, more manageable systems, and greater confidence.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class="mt-10 text-center">
        <a href="/contact"
           class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-extrabold transition hover:brightness-110"
           style="background: var(--color-accent-green); color: #08110c; box-shadow: 0 0 22px rgba(57,255,122,0.22);">
          Discuss the right option
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
